# VEHICLE::CAN_CARGOBOB_PICK_UP_ENTITY

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** cargobob
* **ENTITY_INDEX** entity

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns whether the given entity can be pickup up by the cargobob
